https://www.postgresql.org/docs/14/runtime-config-logging.html#GUC-LOG-LINE-PREFIX

Important to control the logfile size. 

log_line_prefix = '%m [%p] %q%u@%d '

The true nuclear options

ALTER SYSTEM SET log_statement = 'none';
ALTER SYSTEM SET log_min_duration_statement = 200;
ALTER SYSTEM SET log_duration = off;
ALTER SYSTEM SET log_error_verbosity = 'default';
ALTER SYSTEM SET log_statement_stats = off;
ALTER SYSTEM SET log_parser_stats = off;
ALTER SYSTEM SET log_planner_stats = off;
ALTER SYSTEM SET log_executor_stats = off;
SELECT pg_reload_conf();




